This test 
- starts LinuxCNC using test.ini
- uses MDI commands to change the startup state of the modal gcodes
- initializes an interpreter instance to the currently active modal gcodes using the gremlin helper function and loads a test gcode file that lacks a preamble
- checks that the start up state reflects [RS274NGC] RS274NGC_STARTUP_CODE and output of the interpreter after loading the test gcode file.
